Pricing
$109 one-time payment
No recurring fees. No per-account charges. No support contracts. Buy once, use forever.
How To Use It
Initial run
Review all recommendations manually. Understand what the script flags and why.
Implementation
Add negative keywords you agree with. Ignore recommendations you disagree with. You maintain full control.
Ongoing
Run weekly or bi-weekly. Or schedule to run automatically and review results periodically.
Redundant cleanup
Use redundant negative detection quarterly to clean up lists.
Common Questions
Will it add negatives automatically?
No. Provides recommendations only. You review and implement.
