:{"ext":".png","url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/thumbnail_tat_raw_009_animation_55f952a7f9.png","hash":"thumbnail_tat_raw_009_animation_55f952a7f9","mime":"image/png","name":"thumbnail_tat-raw-009-animation.png","path":null,"size":29.87,"width":88,"height":156,"sizeInBytes":29874}},"hash":"tat_raw_009_animation_55f952a7f9","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","size":305.65,"url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/tat_raw_009_animation_55f952a7f9.png","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-cloudflare-r2","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-27T20:47:18.422Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-27T20:47:18.422Z","publishedAt":"2026-03-27T20:47:18.422Z","focalPoint":null}},{"id":96,"caption":null,"class":null,"title":"Hybrid","subtitle":null,"name":"Hybrid","anchor_href":"https://projects.motionapp.com/organization/69441477e6e360bb81e39da8/6944148b22af79295f8edea1/inspo/board/698d32396adcc30b92d8b20f","anchor_target":"_blank","data":{"pill":{"value":"5.74"}},"body":null,"hide":null,"file":{"id":310,"documentId":"cf1tu16kdflqi46557w9e7gy","name":"tat-raw-010-hybrid.png","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"width":316,"height":562,"formats":{"small":{"ext":".png","url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/small_tat_raw_010_hybrid_f25a3d0ccd.png","hash":"small_tat_raw_010_hybrid_f25a3d0ccd","mime":"image/png","name":"small_tat-raw-010-hybrid.png","path":null,"size":240.65,"width":281,"height":500,"sizeInBytes":240654},"thumbnail":{"ext":".png","url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/thumbnail_tat_raw_010_hybrid_f25a3d0ccd.png","hash":"thumbnail_tat_raw_010_hybrid_f25a3d0ccd","mime":"image/png","name":"thumbnail_tat-raw-010-hybrid.png","path":null,"size":30.81,"width":88,"height":156,"sizeInBytes":30809}},"hash":"tat_raw_010_hybrid_f25a3d0ccd","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","size":238.43,"url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/tat_raw_010_hybrid_f25a3d0ccd.png","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-cloudflare-r2","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-27T20:47:17.600Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-27T20:47:17.600Z","publishedAt":"2026-03-27T20:47:17.600Z","focalPoint":null}}],"__component":"shared.media-gallery"},{"id":233,"name":"Top asset types","class":null,"chart":{"id":24,"documentId":"icqii7b3kwa1lybx8ye2c0ed","name":"creative-benchmarks-2026-top-asset-types","createdAt":"2026-03-03T06:26:41.180Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-03T06:28:13.697Z","publishedAt":"2026-03-03T06:28:14.014Z","title":"Creative Benchmarks 2026 - Top Asset Types","subtitle":null},"__component":"shared.chart"},{"id":4032,"body":"Text-forward assets create winners more often than many teams expect. Text-only ads, product images with text overlays, and simple GIFs frequently rank well. Their strength is speed and clarity. They can communicate value quickly and allow small framing changes without reimagining entire campaigns. \n\nBecause they are fast to produce, these assets also make experimentation easier. A team can test multiple variations in a short period, which increases exposure to different outcomes. In a system where rare events matter, the ability to try more variations can influence results.\n\nHigher-production assets play a different role. In some cases, they signal \ncredibility or brand quality. But they are slower to change. When iteration slows, the number of ideas tested often slows as well. That does not make these assets ineffective, but it changes how they function during testing.","class":null,"name":"Text-forward assets create winners ...","title":null,"eyebrow":null,"layout":null,"__component":"shared.rich-text"},{"id":3125,"class":"bubble-caption the-distinction","caption":null,"title":null,"name":"The distinction is not between ...","href":null,"href_target":null,"body":null,"layout":null,"smallscreen":{"id":269,"documentId":"gw2d20wqcxn7n7pjj5hq6fwx","name":"the-distinction-smallscreen.svg","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"width":390,"height":456,"formats":null,"hash":"the_distinction_smallscreen_fe76369ed5","ext":".svg","mime":"image/svg+xml","size":302.38,"url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/the_distinction_smallscreen_fe76369ed5.svg","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-cloudflare-r2","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-04T18:16:19.478Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-04T18:16:19.478Z","publishedAt":"2026-03-04T18:16:19.485Z","focalPoint":null},"image":{"id":266,"documentId":"a6q7yk6rxe1vwu4hz34hz2bf","name":"cb2026-the-distinction.svg","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"width":927,"height":248,"formats":null,"hash":"cb2026_the_distinction_58bc093a08","ext":".svg","mime":"image/svg+xml","size":303.24,"url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/cb2026_the_distinction_58bc093a08.svg","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-cloudflare-r2","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-03T06:30:48.629Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-03T06:30:48.629Z","publishedAt":"2026-03-03T06:30:48.629Z","focalPoint":null},"__component":"shared.image"},{"id":4033,"body":"# Structuring your strategy for success\n\nOne major takeaway from this research is that advertising — and creative strategy — can be humbling.\n\nFor all the planning, optimizing, and iteration, creative performance resists tight control. The system is shaped by human attention, platform dynamics, and competition that never sits still. Outcomes cluster. A few ads carry accounts. Many barely move the needle.\n\nPerformance advertising looks less like careful optimization and more like broad exploration. Not blind guessing, but structured searching in an environment where winning is rare.\n\nThe role of a creative strategist is not to predict the future perfectly. It’s to build conditions where winning ideas can surface, where signals are noticed, and where decisions are made with evidence rather than attachment. \n\nThere is also something reassuring in the benchmarks themselves. They show that uneven win rates are not a personal failing or a team-specific problem. They are a shared reality across thousands of advertisers. The pressure to “crack the code” often oversells how deterministic performance advertising really is.\n\nThe advertisers who win out will not be the ones who eliminate failure. They will be the ones who make it survivable and routine. They’ll keep shipping high volume. They’ll keep adjusting. And they’ll keep looking for a signal in the noise.\n\n## \n\n* Key Benchmarks Summary \n* Full Methodology . \n* Download LLM files ","class":null,"name":"Structuring your strategy for success","title":null,"eyebrow":null,"layout":null,"__component":"shared.rich-text"},{"id":93,"header":"Want to see how your data stacks up to these benchmarks?","body":"Create a free Motion account and our AI will tag your ads based on formats, hooks, asset types - and more - so you can see can close gaps and spot opportunities.","class":"secondies","name":"Want to see how your data stacks up to these benchmarks?","button":[{"id":358,"text":"Book a demo","url":"https://motionapp.com/book-a-demo","buttonstyle":null,"unfurler":false,"target":null},{"id":359,"text":"Start free trial","url":"https://projects.motionapp.com/signup","buttonstyle":"hollow","unfurler":false,"target":null}],"graphical_accompaniment":{"id":3126,"class":null,"caption":null,"title":null,"name":null,"href":null,"href_target":null,"body":null,"layout":null,"image":{"id":232,"documentId":"q3j44qd98whtfmwiiv4eks1v","name":"cb2026-demo-trial-2026-03-02.png","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"width":846,"height":642,"formats":{"small":{"ext":".png","url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/small_cb2026_demo_trial_2026_03_02_a4d69b91ea.png","hash":"small_cb2026_demo_trial_2026_03_02_a4d69b91ea","mime":"image/png","name":"small_cb2026-demo-trial-2026-03-02.png","path":null,"size":320.7,"width":500,"height":379,"sizeInBytes":320696},"medium":{"ext":".png","url":"https://runt-media.motionapp.com/strapi/medium_cb2026_demo_trial_2026_03_02_a4d69b91ea.png","hash":"medium_cb2026_de